    <item>
      <title>特朗普的关税从美国股市浪费了2万亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-tariffs-set-to-zap-nearly-2-trillion-from-us-stock-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，S＆amp; P 500指数从S＆amp; P 500指数中删除了大约2万亿美元，因为担心唐纳德·特朗普总统的新一轮关税可能会使经济陷入衰退。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-tariffs-set-to-zap-nearly-2-trillion-from-us-stock-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 12:00:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>丹麦股票随着关税的关税而滑入熊市市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/denmark-stock-index-set-for-bear-market-as-tariffs-novo-weigh-m91178mq</link>
      <description><![CDATA[丹麦的基准股票指数比9月份的高点下降了21％，这使其成为第一个进入熊市的主要欧洲指数，因为与关税相关的风险和Novo Novo Nordisk A/S的体重下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/denmark-stock-index-set-for-bear-market-as-tariffs-novo-weigh-m91178mq</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 07:25:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>燃料，面包短缺促使莫桑比克FX规则更改</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/dollar-shortage-threatens-bread-and-fuel-supplies-in-mozambique</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫桑比克的中央银行宣布了临时措施，以减轻造成燃料供应的美元紧缩，并威胁要触发东南非洲国家的面包短缺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/dollar-shortage-threatens-bread-and-fuel-supplies-in-mozambique</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着债券的集会，股票途径加深关税冲击：市场包装</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的关税战争的影响周四遍布全球市场，击落股票并促进了进入固定收益避风港的飞行。美国股票和美元对猜测最糟糕的卖出总统的贸易攻势将阻碍美国经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 23:34:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
